This requires a template file name as REF.vasp (it should be the smallest unit-cell or primitive POSCAR)
You need to provide the supercell size (3x3 matrix ) in INP_MDLAB (line number 11-13) used in MD simulation with respect to REF.vasp  
For other tags please refere: https://www.sciencedirect.com/science/article/pii/S0010465525004837
